<div class="item"><span>1080+108💎=45,800Ar</span><button onclick="openForm('1080+108💎=45,800Ar')">Acheter</button></div>

<h3>ABONNEMENT (Par UID)✅</h3>

<div class="item"><span>✨🧨 weekly             450💎    =10.500Ar</span><button onclick="openForm('weekly 450💎=10.500Ar')">Acheter</button></div>
<div class="item"><span>✨🧨 Monthly        2600💎    =48,000Ar</span><button onclick="openForm('Monthly 2600💎=48,000Ar')">Acheter</button></div>

<h3>LEVEL UP (Par UID)✅</h3>

<div class="item"><span>✨0,29 $ ≈ 2,800ar   120💎(niv.6)</span><button onclick="openForm('120💎 niv6 = 2800Ar')">Acheter</button></div>
<div class="item"><span>✨0,50 $ ≈ 3,700ar   200💎(niv10)</span><button onclick="openForm('200💎 niv10 = 3700Ar')">Acheter</button></div>
<div class="item"><span>✨0,50 $ ≈ 3,700ar   200💎(niv15)</span><button onclick="openForm('200💎 niv15 = 3700Ar')">Acheter</button></div>
<div class="item"><span>✨0,50 $ ≈ 3,700ar   200💎(niv20)</span><button onclick="openForm('200💎 niv20 = 3700Ar')">Acheter</button></div>
<div class="item"><span>✨0,50 $ ≈ 3,700ar   200💎(niv25)</span><button onclick="openForm('200💎 niv25 = 3700Ar')">Acheter</button></div>
<div class="item"><span>✨0,79 $ ≈ 5,500ar   350💎(niv 35)</span><button onclick="openForm('350💎 niv35 = 5500Ar')">Acheter</button></div>
